ygData.msgSnippet: Emepror crush doesnt have the axe. But the lord that spawns on the throne. (not dvinn) has a dwarven axe wich is realy nice Vashi
ygData.messageBody:
Emepror crush doesnt have the axe.
But the lord that spawns on the throne. (not dvinn)
has a dwarven axe wich is realy nice

Vashi
